312
00:37:59,601 --> 00:38:03,059
Well, like a parable then.

313
00:38:03,872 --> 00:38:08,176
And it wants to tells us that...
none of the options are good.

314
00:38:08,211 --> 00:38:10,343
Are you sure?

315
00:38:10,378 --> 00:38:12,848
