00:53:54,688 --> 00:53:59,648
Third or fourth option, I don't know
which one, but it is called Graph

514
00:54:00,060 --> 00:54:02,261
Did it work?

515
00:54:02,296 --> 00:54:08,235
Ok, I have to go. Joel is calling me
to go for a walk.

516
00:54:14,608 --> 00:54:16,576
Bye bye

517
00:54:39,667 --> 00:54:41,133
For the cold.

518
00:54:41,168 --> 00:54:43,068
Thank you very much.

