00:55:41,128 --> 00:55:42,595
What?

527
00:55:43,864 --> 00:55:46,833
Doesn't matter, nothing.

528
00:58:51,318 --> 00:58:52,683
Hello!

529
00:58:59,659 --> 00:59:05,562
Carla, do you think that in the future
there will be no more trees?

530
00:59:09,069 --> 00:59:11,867
Eh...I don't think so.

531
00:59:13,841 --> 00:59:17,436
Me neither. There're too many.

532
00:59:29,022 --> 00:59:34,983
When I first came here I saw everything
like a green mass.

533
00:59:35,863 --> 00:59:41,665
Almost exasperating.
I even dreamt in green.

534
00:59:41,969 --> 00:59:46,940
